<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="over-and-over-again">over and over (again)</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>反复；再三：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As you know, if you do the same thing over and over again, you begin to do it automatically.
你知道，如果反反复复地做同样的事，动作就会变得自如起来。</p><footer>人教⑥ – 3</footer></div></div>